<section class="careers-section">
  <div class="content">
    <h1>CAREERS AT MOKAE</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Work With Us. Create With Purpose.</p>
    <p class="description">
      Mokae is a clean, high-performance beauty brand rooted in self-love, holistic well-being, and fearless
      self-expression. We’re building a thoughtful, driven team that believes beauty can be safe, conscious, and
      transformative. If that speaks to you—read on.
    </p>

    <h2>Why Join Us?</h2>
    <ul class="benefits">
      <li><span>•</span> <span>A young and fast-growing beauty brand with big dreams</span> </li>
      <li><span>•</span>  <span>Work that’s rooted in conscious living and clean innovation </span> </li>
      <li><span>•</span> <span> A collaborative culture that values creativity and authenticity </span></li>
      <li><span>•</span>  <span>The opportunity to shape beauty conversations in India and beyond </span></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="list-container">
  <h1 class="title">OPEN POSITIONS</h1>
  <ul class="job-list">
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Jr. Graphic Designer</h2>
      <p>
        Assist in creating digital assets for social media, website, and campaigns. Support the design team with layout,
        visual consistency, and brand-driven creatives.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Creative Head / Sr. Designer</h2>
      <p>
        Lead creative direction across brand and marketing assets—from concept to execution. Manage and mentor the
        design team while maintaining a high visual standard across all touchpoints.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Video Editor</h2>
      <p>
        Edit reels, campaign videos, and tutorial content for digital platforms. Work closely with the creative and
        marketing teams to deliver polished, engaging video content with strong brand alignment.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Brand Manager</h2>
      <p>
        Oversee and execute brand strategy across marketing, product, and content functions. Manage cross-functional
        teams, agency partners, and ensure timely delivery of campaigns and launches.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Social Media Manager</h2>
      <p>
        Plan and manage the content calendar across platforms. Coordinate with the design, content, and influencer teams
        to execute high-impact campaigns and day-to-day engagement.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Content Writer</h2>
      <p>
        Write clear, compelling copy for social media, website, emailers, and product pages. Collaborate with creative
        and marketing teams to maintain a consistent brand voice across all platforms.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Logistics & Supply Chain Manager</h2>
      <p>
        Handle order processing, inventory management, vendor coordination, and dispatch. Manage Shopify backend, track
        shipments, and ensure timely fulfilment with an eye on efficiency and accuracy.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>
        Makeup Artist <br>
        (Retail + Experience Lead)
      </h2>
      <p>
        Conduct product trials, product training, in-person demos, and consultations at pop-ups, events, and
        masterclasses. Ideal for artists who are confident, knowledgeable, and love connecting with people.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="job-item">
      <h2>Marketing & Sales Head</h2>
      <p>
        Drive top-line growth through revenue generation activations like brand campaigns, partnerships. and retail
        initiatives. Develop integrated strategies across channels to build brand equity and increase conversion, with a
        strong focus on data, storytelling, and revenue-driving activities.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <div class="desc-wrap">
    <p>
      P.S. Please apply only if you have relevant experience for the listed roles. To apply, email your CV to
      <a href="mailto:hr@mokaebeauty.com">hr@mokaebeauty.com</a>. <br>
      If your profile aligns with what we’re looking for, our team will get in touch.
    </p>
    <p>
      <span> DON’T SEE A ROLE THAT FITS?</span><br>
      We’re always open to meeting like-minded dreamers and doers. Email us your resume at
      <a href="mailto:hr@mokaebeauty.com">hr@mokaebeauty.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

